  "title": "Makeup Artist cum Therapist (Eyelash & Skincare)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Makeup Artist cum Therapist (Eyelash & Skincare)</strong><br />Working Days & Hours: 6 days | 10:45pm - 8:15pm<br />Location: Nearby Chinatown MRT<br />Salary: $2200 – $2800 + Commission</p><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Provide professional makeup services (events, photoshoots, client sessions)</li><li>Conduct skin analysis & makeup consultation</li><li>Perform head spa treatments & basic scalp massage</li><li>Provide eyelash services (extensions / lifting)</li><li>Perform basic facial & skincare treatment.</li><li>Assist in photography, branding & content shoots</li><li>Recommend and upsell makeup, spa & skincare packages</li><li>Maintain hygiene of brushes, tools & treatment areas</li></ul><p><strong>Requirement</strong></p><ul><li>Certified Makeup Artist preferred</li><li>Experience in beauty / skincare / spa services preferred</li><li>Certification in eyelash or facial treatments is a strong advantage</li></ul><p><strong>Tee Xin Li Reg No: R24121619</strong><br /><strong>The Supreme Hr Advisory Pte Ltd EA No: 14C7279</strong></p>",
